observations.recommendation:
We recommended and management agreed to:

consider the timelines set for the project and improve its monitoring functions or supervision for projects being implemented to avoid incurrence of delays;

strictly adhere to the above-cited provisions of RA No. 9184 and its IRR and the DILG Memorandum Circular respecting documentary requirements and post-completion activities of the project.

We recommended and the Local Chief Executive agreed to:

adopt better planning strategies in order to comprehensively consider all factors in programming, prioritizing and implementing developmental projects;

maximize the use of funds and implement fully the priority programs and projects under the local development fund;

instruct the Bids and Awards Committee and its Secretariat to strictly adhere to the above-cited provisions of RA No. 9184 and its IRR and the COA Circular 2012-01 respecting documentary requirements; and

require the Bids and Awards Committee, Engineering Office and Accounting Office to submit immediately the absent documents above-mentioned.

